Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那麼…為慶祝大家第一次聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 這人還真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不直接去把下一層的boss也打了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了
